# chesscoach-gateway is its own private repo (see chesscoach-gateway/README.md
# for why it's separate: GPLv3 disclosure boundary). It lives here on disk for
# convenience but is never part of this (public) repo's history.
chesscoach-gateway/

# chesscoach-website is likewise its own separate private repo (see
# chesscoach-website/README.md) -- pure marketing/legal content, no reason to
# be open source, and kept separate from chesscoach-gateway too so routine
# copy changes don't add review overhead to the payment-critical service.
chesscoach-website/

# Playwright MCP debug artifacts (screenshots/snapshots/console logs from
# ad hoc browser verification) -- ephemeral, never meant to be committed.
.playwright-mcp/
